{"tid":2509310,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"HKCC 2020-2021 討論區【52】光復香港 時代革命","createTime":"2021-04-29T10:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T17:56:24.000Z","uid":233679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e555d26372a335c8eadcdb8d21b85e4601f186","tid":2509310,"uid":233679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:32:00.000Z","msg":"學術類<br />\nSem：Semester 學期，一學年最多有3個Sem<br />\nSem 1：9至12月 - 13 Teaching Weeks<br />\nSem 2：1至4月 - 13 Teaching Weeks<br />\nSummer Term：6至8月 - 7 Teaching Weeks<br />\n^Year 1 Sem1所有Tutorial都會係同同一班人一齊上，係識朋友嘅好機會<br />\n<br />\nLecture：教書堂，一般兩小時，部分科目達三小時<br />\nTutorial：溫書堂，做Exercise/做Presentation/Review返Lecture講過嘅嘢，大概有25人1個Tutor<br />\nLecturer：負責教你嗰科嘅老師<br />\nMid-term：通常考返Week 1-6內容嘅測驗，佔Coursework嘅30-50%不等<br />\nFinal：Final examination，佔整科0%/40%-50%<br />\nSit堂：上其他lecturer/同一個lecturer其他時間嘅堂(通常Sit得都係唔得閒上自己個時間/ 你個lecturer太廢)<br />\nDay-off：星期一至五其中一日無堂上<br />\n<br />\nGrade：每一科之成績，A+ = 4.3, A = 4.0, A-= 3.7, B+ = 3.3, B = 3.0, B-=2.7, C+ = 2.3, C = 2.0, C-= 1.7, D+ = 1.3, D= 1.0 ,F = 0；並非所有科有派A+，例如英文<br />\nGPA：Grade Point Average，一個學期之所有grade加總/該學期科目總數<br />\nCGPA：Cumulative Grade Point Average，所有Grade加總除一共上過嘅科目總數<br />\nCGPA最少 1.70先可以順利繼續讀,低過 1.70 要 academic probation,要減 workload, retake 某一些科<br />\n連續兩個 sem 低過 1.70 CC唔會俾你讀落去<br />\nCredit：多數科係3個Credits；1個Sem大概讀15個credits，下限12、上限18 ( AE 4 credits)<br />\nGE Subjects：通識科目，所有學生須在5個類別科目中選讀至少4個類別之科 (其中一個要 China- related)<br />\nDS Subject：所屬Programme之下的必須科目<br />\nReg科：每個sem 約Week 6開始，揀下一個sem之科目<br />\nAdd/Drop：揀Timeslot/老師/科，每班限人數，經常出現0 Vacancy(空缺)，要鬥快Reg入去心儀班次，Sem頭開放Add/Drop，具體請留意Email及內附嘅Guide To Add/Drop<br />\n^Year 1 Sem 1冇得Reg科及Add/Drop<br />\n<br />\nTranscript：成績表，可經myhkcc申請，每張$70<br />\nTurnitin：Check你份Assignment有冇抄人(Plagiarism)<br />\nConsultation Hours：每個老師每個禮拜總共有3小時在Office等你，可以問書、舉報freerider等等<br />\nPart-time lecturer 可能只能用電話問問題<br />\nFreerider：對份Project無/少貢獻嘅人，明明唔做嘢但係又好厚面皮咁痴住你去攞分<br />\n^如果想舉報freerider，請搜集好證據 (例如：WhatsApp Cap圖，Google Drive修改記錄等)<br />\nKiller：意指專出爛Grade之Lecturer<br />\n<br />\n校園組織類及其他<br />\nCAT：Co-curriculum Achievements Transcript，活動紀錄(並非所有活動都會有CAT)；HKCC有獎學金比儲CAT的人<br />\nCFM校園設施管理辦事處：WK @ SLG/F、HHB @ LG/F，物品報失請往CFM<br />\nCSAO(CPCE Student Affairs Office)：處理學生活動成績表嘅Order，多數活動申請表都係呢度交；位於WK @ N3/F、HHB @ 4樓<br />\nFSCC(Further Studies and Career Centre)：入面有關於升學/搵工嘅資訊，有本薄仔有畢業生資料 (例如GPA+programme+interview details+佢收到咩offer)<br />\nIK(詢問處)：WK @ N2/F、HHB UG/F，主要喺度交文件<br />\nITU：IT Unit，負責處理所有IT問題，Counter設於網吧門口<br />\nPDA(Personal Development Area)：由CSAO開設，可以搵到社工傾計"},{"pid":"9a426efc590ac9e708302765df75f96bd828bddb","tid":2509310,"uid":233679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:32:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><span class=\"x-large\">會員編號：310275<br />\n會員名稱：駿羊局焗腸<br />\n註冊日期：2019年8月20日</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">【狗隻】<br />\n事蹟：恥笑被還押的連登仔 (椰子是無辜的)。</span><br />\n詳細來源：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aHMKnMV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aHMKnMV</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">【⚠️】<br />\n事蹟：嘲諷12位被送中手足，話「Save12,終於送返入監倉夠晒safe」</span><br />\n詳細來源：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2456407/page/2?post=40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2456407/page/2?post=40</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">【⚠️】<br />\n事蹟：話19年香港反送中人士係義和團</span><br />\n詳細來源：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2461040/page/4?post=89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2461040/page/4?post=89</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">【⚠️】<br />\n事蹟：緬甸示威者死被殺，佢話「所以關我咩事？一係送晒佢哋全家落去一齊團聚？」</span><br />\n詳細來源：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2471461/page/3?post=75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2471461/page/3?post=75</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">見到五毛、藍絲、狗隻、引戰狗唔該直接block and ignore</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">P.S. 被標記為【⚠️】唔一定係五毛，但一定係戇鳩(部分出自power_off嘅on9list)，可以畀大家認識到比較特別嘅會員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e2e6a8b3703640be7b68e0bb330a3593d01ce489","tid":2509310,"uid":233679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:32:45.000Z","msg":"有用連結<br />\nCFM網站 - Lost and Found List及Shuttle班次 : <a href=\"https://cfm.cpce-polyu.edu.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcfm.cpce-polyu.edu.hk&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=ee6113d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cfm.cpce-polyu.edu.hk</a><br />\n玻璃房(小組研習室)Booking : <a href=\"https://mbs.cpce-polyu.edu.hk/ibooking/booking.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmbs.cpce-polyu.edu.hk%2Fibooking%2Fbooking.php&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=558a8d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mbs.cpce-polyu.edu.hk/ibooking/booking.php</a><br />\n校園設施Booking : <a href=\"https://sao.cpce-polyu.edu.hk/facilities-campus.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsao.cpce-polyu.edu.hk%2Ffacilities-campus.php&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=d656f1c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sao.cpce-polyu.edu.hk/facilities-campus.php</a><br />\nEmail：經常有重要嘢，記得留意Email，HKCC用全套Office 365，所以係Outlook同OneDrive而冇免費Google Drive<br />\n兩個校園附近極多巴士，而且好多你未必知，記得Check下<br />\n<br />\nHKCC用語及設施一覽：<br />\n校園及交通<br />\n括號內指步行所需時間 (分鐘)<br />\nHHB：紅磡灣校園 - Science/Engine/IT/Design嘅Home Campus<br />\n最近港鐵站：黃埔(5)/紅磡(10)<br />\n鄰近巴士站：海韻軒(九巴稱紅樂道，設115特快去銅鑼灣、灣仔、中上環)<br />\n值得搭嘅巴士路線：門口就有115特快去銅鑼灣 灣仔 中上環、或到紅隧口大量往港島及九龍新界巴士<br />\n<br />\nWK：西九龍校園，分南、北兩座，只有部份樓層南北相通 - Business/文科嘅Home Campus<br />\n最近港鐵站：油麻地(12-15)/奧運(10)<br />\n鄰近巴士站：柏景灣總站、西九龍站總站(10-12)、富榮花園、欣翔道(步程約10分鐘，有280X直入沙田、271X直入大埔)、佐敦道巴士站(步程約15分鐘，有970(X)/973直入西隧、E23(A)直入東涌、260X直入屯門、268/9B直入欖隧<br />\n<br />\n值得搭嘅巴士路線：W2、W3（臨時暫停服務直至另行通知）、2E 土瓜灣/馬頭圍/石硤尾、12、914、城巴20(可轉乘A22往九龍灣、796C/796X往將軍澳或轉車站)同埋欣翔道或佐敦道巴士站上面提過嘅巴士<br />\n<br />\nShuttle：免費來往WK &lt;&gt; PolyU &lt;&gt; HHB之穿梭巴士，Express班次不經PolyU，時間表於CPCE CFM網站及Shuttle站，WK過海可善用Shuttle到紅隧口搭車<br />\n<br />\n校園設施<br />\n想搵地方傾Project/食飯/做功課/Hea嘅話可以考慮下一啲周圍嘅枱，例如WK S7咁，除咗圓枱之外都有插座<br />\n圖書館(拉把)：<br />\nHKCC學生可以用PolyU本部嘅包玉剛圖書館 / WK / HHB 圖書館<br />\n<br />\nWK - 入口及Counter @ N5/F<br />\n4樓：電腦房、圓枱、玻璃房<br />\n5樓：電腦、Printer、入口、借書還書借Reserve書Counter<br />\n6樓：藏書區、電腦、自修用座位、玻璃房(備有電腦及圓枱)<br />\n<br />\nHHB - 入口及Counter @ 10樓<br />\n9樓：藏書區、電腦、自修用座位、玻璃房(備有電腦及圓枱)<br />\n10樓：電腦、Printer、入口、借書還書借Reserve書Counter、玻璃房(位於圖書館入口對面，長期開放)<br />\n<br />\n^Exam Period嘅星期日及公眾假期，可以用貨Lift到WK 4樓溫書<br />\n<br />\n學生電腦中心(網吧)：WK @ S5/F、HHB @ 11樓，提供電腦及Printer，並有Notebook及iPad租借服務，亦設有Printing Quota增值機<br />\n<br />\nPrint嘢<br />\n每一學年自動補充至2200 Quota，每個Quota增值要$0.1<br />\nPrint每張黑白A4扣2個Quota，留意彩色Printer即使Print黑白照扣彩色價(15 Quota)<br />\nExpress Printing Area設於WK S1/F、N7/F、S9/F，HHB 1樓、3樓、6樓，亦可到拉把/網吧Print<br />\n<br />\nMPH/Hall(禮堂)： WK @ SUG/F、HHB @ 1樓，可以利用上面Link Book場<br />\n舞蹈室(鏡房)：WK @ NUG/F、HHB @ 2樓，可以利用上面Link Book場<br />\n明日：24小時開放，WK @ S2/F、HHB @ UG樓；備有叉電座嘅六角枱 - 實際上好嘈及好多MK長期霸佔，不宜傾Project<br />\nPacific Coffee及7-ELEVEN：WK @ S3/F、HHB @ 4樓 - Pacific Coffee華潤國企不了，另外熱賣點會早啲收<br />\n學生保健中心(獸醫)：WK @ NLG/F (上9-13樓升降機隔離)、HHB @ LG/F ，$15睇1次醫生 - 盈健營運，喺其他盈健診所有優惠價，大約$170<br />\n<br />\n網上資源<br />\nmyHKCC：Add/Drop、睇自己時間表/GPA、睇Exam日期等<br />\nCARES @ myHKCC：用作報義工/Talk/課外活動之用及HM報Hotel Stay之用<br />\nMoodle：科目分發學科資源及交功課之用"},{"pid":"602f3f9e1cc832ee55ccfa22ef2dc2957261c0d6","tid":2509310,"uid":233679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:33:01.000Z","msg":"繼續屌你老母清單：<br />\n<br />\nHKCC高層 + ITU + SU<br />\n<br />\n鄧力恆<br />\n<br />\nAngel So<br />\n<br />\nErwin Lau<br />\n<br />\nKent Lam<br />\n<br />\n陳偉強<br />\n<br />\nHelen Yeh<br />\n<br />\nWinfred Xuan<br />\n<br />\nJennifer Leong<br />\n<br />\nLancy Tsang<br />\n<br />\nPauline Ho<br />\n<br />\nPamela Ho<br />\n<br />\nSandy Hui￼￼￼￼<br />\n<br />\nJack Chow￼教書廢又手緊，出卷又閪，放過請槍班人<br />\n<br />\nCarmen Lee<br />\n<br />\n既然有咗屌你老母清單，當然要有埋好人一生平安清單。證明我哋喺高質嘅學生￼<br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安清單：<br />\nLo Ching On<br />\n<br />\nCrystal Lee Yan Pui<br />\n<br />\nBarbara Ngai<br />\n<br />\n貝剛毅<br />\n<br />\nAda Chan<br />\n<br />\nSquare Ho<br />\n<br />\n蔡維玉<br />\n<br />\nSylvia Ng<br />\n<br />\nLing Chan<br />\n<br />\nTimothy Ngan<br />\n<br />\nOscar Chiu<br />\n<br />\nRicky Mak<br />\n<br />\nJanice Choi<br />\n<br />\nAlan Chan<br />\n<br />\nJodie Lee<br />\n<br />\n朱寶盈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAngel So N宗罪<br />\n1. 有錯唔肯認<br />\n2. 教書照稿讀<br />\n3. 有事就話學生唔體諒<br />\n4. 提醒佢就屌返人轉頭<br />\n5. 做嘢唔撚用腦<br />\n6. Moodle documents 1999<br />\n7. Last minute 先腥email<br />\n8. 成日都好忙但唔知忙咩<br />\n9. 平時email唔覆 連轉科email都唔覆<br />\n10.態度閪<br />\n11.成日將啲唔重要嘅嘢重複講幾次<br />\n12.話要告鳩啲學生喺連登屌佢<br />\n13.成日認屎認屁 話自己好撚叻<br />\n各位唔想喺有生之年俾衰過pat屎嘅lecturer教就千祈唔好reg佢<br />\n<br />\nSandy Hui N宗罪<br />\n1. 身為subject leader成日呻自己好多嘢做好辛苦，例如要逐個逐個document放上moodle，成個怨婦咁<br />\n2. 性格閪<br />\n3. Kill<br />\n4. 出卷閪<br />\n5. 扣埋曬啲唔合理分，2個lecturer求情都堅持扣埋濕鳩嘢<br />\n6. Set個arrangement同課程set到on99，例如日文1唔教片假名<br />\n7. 上堂要答問題 唔係度要扣participation分 (去廁所或者斟杯水miss左 就可以同participation分講byebye)<br />\n<br />\nCarmen Lee N 宗罪<br />\n1. 上堂唔備課, 照書讀<br />\n2. 英文極其差<br />\n3. 講嘢1999, 係咁Eerrer, 好多胃氣￼￼<br />\n4. 改卷慢, Assignment 拖過年先派Grade<br />\n5. 笑騎騎, 放爛Grade<br />\n6. Killer<br />\n7. 上堂一有人講野就禁出去Chat room讀人個內容阻住課堂進度<br />\n8. 讀Chatbox 揼波鐘揼完場"},{"pid":"3b629af1149d4ec232a73ad91091d0b3da458c2f","tid":2509310,"uid":233679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"以下Q&amp;A適用於所有HKCC學生<br />\n<br />\nQ1. 咩叫死亡鐵三角？<br />\nA: 所謂死亡鐵三角，是指LCH1105 大專中文傳意，SHDH1004 Creative and Critical Thinking 及2科英文（English for Academic Studies I&amp;II/Academic English I&amp;II）<br />\n<br />\n*已確定2018/19學年開始英文2咗嘅新同學要讀Academic English I&amp;II而非EAS<br />\n<br />\n(利申：18-19 FM)<br />\n<br />\nQ2. 點解叫死亡鐵三角？<br />\nA: 主要係因為依3科爛grade機會比較大<br />\n中文<br />\n主要用普通話上，唔排除有lecturer間唔中用粵語，但假若你聽唔明普通話，可以準備全個sem坐係到自修，而且end-term好撚多濕勁野考，包括考你寫簡體字，而呢科最高grade係A (聽聞2017/18 Sem1 有人A+)；<br />\nEAS<br />\n學起上黎就冇咩難度，但份mid-term真係偏難，mean得50分到，英文底唔好既依關都幾難過，呢科最高grade都係A，但得3%人拎；<br />\nCCT/CET<br />\n對concept夠清嘅人嚟講係可以好淺，但對某d人嚟講係好難，讀落去先會知道自己究竟明唔明CCT/CET講乜。唔明白既話，你份mid-/end-term MC有機會一題都唔識做，最高個grade派到A+<br />\n<br />\nQ3. 死亡鐵三角嘅grade爛咗可唔可以retake搏靚grade?<br />\nA: 中文同英文唔會fail你，就算比個爛grade你都一定要你pass，所以冇得retake而CCT/CET(?)就可以retake<br />\n<br />\nQ4. 咩grade先retake到？<br />\n<del>A: C+或以上retake嘅機會都比較微，C/D/D+就比較大機會但都要睇下多唔多F嘅人retake；你話你B/B+都想retake嘅話就視乎個科多唔多人F，位會俾咗低grade嘅人先，真人真事有人MO B左都俾佢retake</del><br />\n<br />\nQ5.點樣申請retake?<br />\nA: 去ik搵佢拎Form 31 - Application for Retaking Subjects / Taking Unqualified Subjects，填完交返比ik等佢批，記得講清楚係拎邊份，有兩個版本<br />\n1. retake passed subject；2. retake failed subject<br />\n<br />\nQ6. Retake要幾錢？<br />\nA: 每科$5,790<br />\n<br />\nQ7. 幾時俾retake既錢？<br />\nA: 報咗名先，上到mid term前嘅幾堂就會有交錢個deadline，好似平時交學費咁交<br />\n<br />\nQ8. Retake有冇得reg時間/lecturer?<br />\nA: 視乎個科多唔多人retake，睇佢開幾多班，原先教你個lecturer未必會係Summer Term再教<br />\n<br />\nQ9. Retake既mid-term/final係幾時?<br />\nA: 6月中開始，7月中mid-term，8月頭final，8月尾放GPA<br />\n<br />\nQ10. 應唔應該讀Summer Term?<br />\nA: Summer Term專門用嚟俾retake嘅同學讀，retake就唔多講；如果你因為想Sem3讀少一科，即係Sem3讀四科，或者英文2咗Sem3要讀6科，Summer Term可以比你讀定其中一科先令自己Sem3冇咁chur<br />\n*Summer Term係比較chur嘅，有可能會係夜晚上堂，例如5PM-9PM (lecture tutorial連住上)，每個禮拜2堂<br />\n<br />\nQ11. 點樣睇Summer Term有咩科可以讀/time slot/幾時deadline<br />\nA: 可讀嘅科目，幾時截止同幾時開sem嘅日子年年不一，想讀Summer Term請check實自己學生email<br />\n<br />\nQ12. 進步獎/HKCC金銀銅獎/政府Outstanding Performance Scholarship (OPS)點申請?<br />\nA: HKCC提名，唔洗申請，等email就得<br />\n<br />\nQ13. 英文好係咪有優勢?<br />\nA: 英文好確實有優勢，但唔讀書都係冇用，有人DSE英文攞5，EAS都係拎B，講左咩自己參透下<br />\n<br />\nQ14. Year-1唔過3，係咪quit得?<br />\nA: 我同你講你可以咁做，但亦有唔少人Year-1唔過3而Sem3&amp;4爆4最後有UGC offer，以上嘅例子多不勝數，但講完你聽而又唔讀書，咁最後有上面嘅例子"},{"pid":"7296d8713619b493769debb3fad1e272d69168ee","tid":2509310,"uid":233679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:33:42.000Z","msg":"cut off表<br />\n<br />\n填分呢到<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfnzEWxHTBbDREdikD4NKojjtD9vTLCDGr126XYMZ-NEB5_Vg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfnzEWxHTBbDREdikD4NKojjtD9vTLCDGr126XYMZ-NEB5_Vg%2Fviewform&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=c84be623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfnzEWxHTBbDREdikD4NKojjtD9vTLCDGr126XYMZ-NEB5_Vg/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n睇分呢到<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/12oXzWOWpAfYSkB792gJ5uQIQkty3RMET_Bz1guDEjLc/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F12oXzWOWpAfYSkB792gJ5uQIQkty3RMET_Bz1guDEjLc%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=fd79a503\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/12oXzWOWpAfYSkB792gJ5uQIQkty3RMET_Bz1guDEjLc/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"168361ad90e7e75220f8d3c35269821f11af903c","tid":2509310,"uid":233679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:34:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWY2RdMRe7kPcCzTk1hZeJmzJaWKrtrkFQPX6iB7jnPJW?filename=dtP7M3h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdtP7M3h.jpg&h=f85e6d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我真係恭喜你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"47af395fa90e9543ec05497ded1c1f0d34b0f09e","tid":2509310,"uid":233679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHKCC Sample:<br />\nSubject: Complaint letter against Chung Yan Lam&rsquo;s behavior<br />\n<br />\nDear sir,<br />\n<br />\nMy name is __, and I am a year two student at HKCC. I am writing to complain about the academic dishonesty behavior that Chung Yan Lam did. All students in HKCC are hard-working in order to have a good grade and get into the university. However, Chung Yan Lam revealed that she has been hiring test takers to finish her assignments and examinations. It is a serious problem that needs to be solved.<br />\n<br />\nIn recent, Chung posted the limited time dynamic about seeking the test takers for hire. You can have a look according to the photos that have been provided in the appendix. That makes a question for us that she finishes her works by finding a test taker. And it is absolutely a behavior that affects academic integrity and academic honesty.<br />\n<br />\nI am very sorry to say, but this kind of behavior must not be appeared by any student in a school of good reputation. Chung, through her behavior, is causing disastrous for the school and its good reputation. In order to solve this crisis, I would like to suggest some solutions such as re-examine her assignment and invite her to have a face-to-face exam.<br />\n<br />\nYou are requested to look into the matter personally and resolve our issue as soon as possible. Academic integrity and academic honesty are central to the mission of HKCC. Owing to the suspected cheating behavior of Chung, we shall not be able to feel honesty and integrity in our school anymore. I hope after receiving this letter, you will take the necessary steps as soon as possible to cope with the unfairness.<br />\n<br />\nyour sincerely<br />\n______</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4aebc140c89ea97a8c495d92f091130594b2b6bf","tid":2509310,"uid":332494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:35:57.000Z","msg":"lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae6fef5e5ac90c7c3dd5905b85cc60275a52f25","tid":2509310,"uid":332162,"like