\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />低分到一個點"},{"pid":"179661565bb34676f59a05105358a72dd7d6da09","tid":2509310,"uid":321117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d608fd6b99b4f01dca99592098a19c570cf7864f","tid":2509310,"uid":162811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:49:24.000Z","msg":"新人lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4adf553281d28396939d1054d9f51f3c6dddb73","tid":2509310,"uid":165364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:55:09.000Z","msg":"LM <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6058b4f65d56ecd69c7952dffbf4bc841a771cf","tid":2509310,"uid":135265,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"各位cc同學，一票不投SU，請連反對票都唔好投，只要佢地過咗有效票數800票，而贊成多於反對，佢地就上硬SU。即使你堅持要投票，請你同啲friend講埋點解要投反對票，r佢地嗰票反對票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果佢地話唔投會斷莊，下屆會俾NDS同學乘虛而入。呢啲說話千祈唔好信，佢地言而無信，有SU同冇SU一鳩樣<br />\n<br />\n同埋，上年唔係有條友話佢地無實權，要改會章要結構性改變咩？佢地有冇做過嘢？增加SU透明度呢？成個SU冇透明度，直情隱埋形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現屆SU上年話要引入小店，取代pacific。今年就話原來校方同佢續咗約，SU莊就問是否支持引入小店。我想講嘅唔係政策重覆，而係證明SU得諮詢功能，唔好笑，雖然佢地唔做嘢而冇實權，咁你冇bargaining power我投你做咩？<br />\n<br />\n<del>而直到今日2021年4月20日上午10點27分都未有一份完整政綱post出嚟，</del>投票唔淨只投立場同理念，仲要睇佢地政綱。佢地言之無物，sell你地投票同呃票冇分別，仲衰過開空頭支票。再次懇請各位一票不投SU，請繼續杯葛選舉<br />\n<br />\n改一改最後一段，是其是，非其非，人地喺<span class=\"red\">第一次投票最後一日凌晨</span>喺CC公海post咗完整政綱，費事人地話我地鳩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n向SU莊講一句，如果啲人唔出嚟投票，係因為你地做得差先唔投票。唔好瀨地硬啦，屌人盲目跟風，你睇吓你地支莊IVP投票期都夠膽去山頂玩，呢票投得落手嘅我心悅誠服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">一票不投SU，全面杯葛選舉</span>"},{"pid":"9ee190d6891f082847377bd4e282ec87cb4952f7","tid":2509310,"uid":332494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d608fd6b99b4f01dca99592098a19c570cf7864f","tid":2509310,"uid":162811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:49:24.000Z","msg":"新人lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a11c4a81efc5b3028495e99f4342f5ba46377c1","tid":2509310,"uid":162811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ee190d6891f082847377bd4e282ec87cb4952f7","tid":2509310,"uid":332494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d608fd6b99b4f01dca99592098a19c570cf7864f","tid":2509310,"uid":162811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:49:24.000Z","msg":"新人lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c7c62f8215315c48968d37237428eaab5316dc","tid":2509310,"uid":255528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a11c4a81efc5b3028495e99f4342f5ba46377c1","tid":2509310,"uid":162811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ee190d6891f082847377bd4e282ec87cb4952f7","tid":2509310,"uid":332494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d608fd6b99b4f01dca99592098a19c570cf7864f","tid":2509310,"uid":162811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:49:24.000Z","msg":"新人lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"